					<description><![CDATA[Rigging your environment works 100% of the time. When I&#039;m in a place that supports health and makes life simple, like during my recent 35-day trip on an island, I automatically lived differently and became a new person overnight regardless of the habits I had living here in the states being in a city. 

Never considered how this happened, but this equation hits it completely. The purpose of my trip was for personal &#038; spiritual growth (Person) and I was in nature with whole organic raw foods and with an older, wiser mentor (Environment). My Behavior was totally conducive and aligned with the learning that transpired there.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Rigging your environment works 100% of the time. When I&#8217;m in a place that supports health and makes life simple, like during my recent 35-day trip on an island, I automatically lived differently and became a new person overnight regardless of the habits I had living here in the states being in a city. </p>
<p>Never considered how this happened, but this equation hits it completely. The purpose of my trip was for personal &amp; spiritual growth (Person) and I was in nature with whole organic raw foods and with an older, wiser mentor (Environment). My Behavior was totally conducive and aligned with the learning that transpired there.</p>
